title: Maj. Lindsay "MAD" Johnson fini flight [Image 4 of 6]
text:
Friends and family spray U.S. Air Force Maj. Lindsay “MAD” Johnson, 357th Fighter Squadron instructor pilot, with water and champagne after her final flight in an A-10C Thunderbolt II aircraft at Davis-Monthan Air Force Base, Arizona, April 4, 2025. The spray-down was a fini flight tradition in the military. (U.S. Air Force photo by Senior Airman Devlin Bishop)
